-- Explosion at Russian Siberian Base Near China Kills Six, Interfax Reports
-- Anastasia Ustinova
-- 2010-07-05T04:31:42Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-05/explosion-at-russian-siberian-base-near-china-kills-six-interfax-reports.html

          
          
             An explosion at a military base in
southern Siberia killed at least six soldiers, Interfax said.  
 The blast occurred in the Altai region, which borders
China, Kazakhstan and Mongolia, the Russian news service said,
without providing any more details immediately.  
